## Customer Segmentation Analysis

### Customer Profile by Value

<<chart: doughnut>>
  data: [45, 32, 15, 8]
  labels: ["High Value (>$50K)", "Medium Value ($10K-$50K)", "Low Value ($1K-$10K)", "Freemium (<$1K)"]
